WEBVTT

00:01.250 --> 00:02.710
《越狱》  前情提要
Previousely On Prison Break.

00:03.000 --> 00:04.140
这才是"锡拉"
This is Sylly

00:04.370 --> 00:07.260
你们是出不去的
You are not even close to get out of here

00:07.500 --> 00:09.600
-爸爸  是我  -丽莎
Dad, it's me.  Lisa

00:09.620 --> 00:12.040
我在枪口上  是唐克雷蒂
I'm at gun point It's Tancredit

00:12.360 --> 00:14.430
她说  你要是不让迈克尔和其他人
She says if you don't,let Michael and the others

00:14.500 --> 00:16.670
带着"锡拉"离开  她就杀了我
leave with Scylla, she'll kill me.

00:18.070 --> 00:19.000
别动
Don't!

00:22.430 --> 00:23.370
我要走了
I'm leaving.

00:23.430 --> 00:24.330
不  怀特先生
No, Mr. White!

00:26.970 --> 00:28.030
转过去
Turn around!

00:28.100 --> 00:29.900
轻点  甜心
Gentle now, sugar.

00:29.970 --> 00:32.970
我是米里亚姆·贺尔兹探员  甜心
That's Special Agent Miriam Holtz to you, sugar.

00:33.030 --> 00:34.170
我们拿到了
We have it!

00:34.230 --> 00:34.770
他们拿到了
They got it.

00:34.830 --> 00:36.900
我没想到 你能查到这么深
I never thought you'd make it this far.

00:36.970 --> 00:38.030
我错了
I was wrong.

00:38.100 --> 00:39.230
怎样
What now?

00:39.300 --> 00:41.070
这是你们的迁移文件
This is all your transfer paperwork.

00:41.130 --> 00:43.100
我得尽快赶到达洛斯那边去
I need to get to Dallow, ASAP.

00:45.230 --> 00:46.270
格雷琴呢
What happened to Gretchen?

00:46.330 --> 00:48.030
她跑了
She got away.

00:55.670 --> 00:56.800
赛尔夫
Self.

01:00.000 --> 01:00.930
赛尔夫[又意:自私鬼]
Self.

01:12.570 --> 01:13.600
他骗了我们
He screwed us.

01:13.670 --> 01:15.100
赛尔夫不能这么做
Self can't do that.

01:15.170 --> 01:17.600
他是政府人员  想干什么都行
He's government. He can do what he pleases.

01:26.100 --> 01:26.970
车一定会来的
The vans are coming.

01:27.030 --> 01:28.270
肯定是耽误了
They're just late.

01:28.270 --> 01:29.530
他不会回来了
He ain't coming back!

01:29.530 --> 01:31.130
你也不确定  林肯  他们会来的
You don't know that, Linc! They're coming!

01:31.200 --> 01:32.930
我们现在怎么办
What do we do now?

01:34.500 --> 01:38.430
给国安局打电话  看他们对赛尔夫了解多少
Call Homeland. See how much they know about Self.

01:41.030 --> 01:42.500
斯坦顿
Stanton.

01:42.570 --> 01:45.700
贺勃  是斯科菲尔德和布伦斯
Herb, it was Scofield and Burrows.

01:45.770 --> 01:47.130
你在议员的办公室吗
Are you at the Senator's office?

01:47.200 --> 01:48.330
我中枪了
I think I'm shot!

01:48.400 --> 01:50.470
我中枪了
I'm shot!

01:50.530 --> 01:53.270
米里亚姆也死了  你听见吗
Miriam's gone, okay?

01:53.330 --> 01:54.430
你在什么地方
What's your position?

01:54.500 --> 01:58.030
这整个行动 你说的是对的
You were right about this whole operation.

01:58.100 --> 02:01.170
不要  布伦斯  布伦斯
No. Burrows, Burrows!

02:01.170 --> 02:03.170
唐
Don.

02:05.330 --> 02:06.500
不妙
No!

02:07.570 --> 02:13.530
我要找格雷琴 你会帮我吗
I need to find Gretchen. You gonna help me?

02:13.600 --> 02:15.800
否则  我让你脸上开花
Or you gonna make me shoot you in the face?

02:15.870 --> 02:18.500
帮[又意:救命]
Help.

02:20.100 --> 02:22.170
国土安全局
Department of Homeland Security.

02:22.230 --> 02:25.030
我找唐·赛尔夫的上司  谢谢
I'd like to talk to Don Self's superior, please.

02:25.100 --> 02:27.130
请稍等
One moment, please.

02:27.200 --> 02:31.630
我们把价值一亿的东西 就这么拱手送给这家伙了
We gave this guy something worth $100 million.

02:31.700 --> 02:33.730
他是国安局的吗  我们看过他的徽章吗
Is he even with Homeland? Did we see a badge?

02:33.800 --> 02:35.830
他给了我们枪  用C-130运输机送我们过来
We were given guns and flown out on a C-130.

02:35.900 --> 02:38.400
-他肯定不是车管局的 -这也不代表他是合法的
He didn't work for the DMV. That doesn't make him the law.

02:38.470 --> 02:39.670
不  不能
No, it don't.

02:39.730 --> 02:42.400
要是国安局从一开始就参与了呢
What if Homeland was in on this from the beginning?

02:42.470 --> 02:44.330
我是贺勃·斯坦顿  你是谁
This is Herb Stanton. Who is this?

02:47.330 --> 02:49.330
喂
Hello?

02:50.300 --> 02:53.170
我搞不清赛尔夫是怎么设的局
The way Self played this, I don't know.

02:53.230 --> 02:54.570
他一直让自己置身事外
He kept himself too insulated.

02:54.630 --> 02:56.700
这就是为什么 需要政府授权时
That's why, that's why he hesitated with official authorizations

02:56.770 --> 02:59.530
他总是犹豫 他总是说  这是为了防止
on behalf of our mission. He kept saying it was because he didn't want

02:59.600 --> 03:01.000
"公司"发现  而实际上
the Company to find out. In actuality,

03:01.070 --> 03:02.700
他是不想让人发现他的诡计
it's because he didn't want to get caught,

03:02.770 --> 03:03.900
狗娘养的
the son of a bitch!

03:03.970 --> 03:07.170
他部署周密 让我们去承担责任
He kept the circle tight. Left the rest of us holding the bag.

03:07.230 --> 03:12.000
如果国安局知道我们在哪 他们迟早会来抓我们
If Homeland knows where we're at. Sooner or later they're coming for us.

03:12.000 --> 03:15.070
让他们来吧 我们又没做错什么  我们有协议的
Let them come. we didn't do anything wrong. We have deals.

03:15.130 --> 03:16.530
不  我们只有白纸  赛尔夫留给我们的
No, we have paper. That's what Self left us.

03:16.600 --> 03:17.570
我们只有这些
That's what we have.

03:17.630 --> 03:19.570
我们得离开这里
We gotta get out of here.

03:19.630 --> 03:21.530
我们不能走  迈克尔需要做手术
We can't leave. Michael needs surgery.

03:23.830 --> 03:24.830
我说的不是逃跑
I'm not talking about running.

03:24.900 --> 03:27.300
我说的是活命
I'm talking about surviving.

03:35.600 --> 03:40.330
我想要的是目睹"公司"土崩瓦解
What I want is to see the Company burned to the ground

03:40.430 --> 03:42.630
而你  锒铛入狱
and you in prison.

03:45.370 --> 03:49.070
这是我们干的  我们干的
We did this to you. We did this to you.

03:57.870 --> 04:00.770
他们正在楼下等你  长官
They're ready for you downstairs, sir.

04:09.000 --> 04:14.600
今天是我们所有努力的关键时刻
Today marks a critical juncture in our endeavor.

04:14.670 --> 04:17.500
有没有"锡拉"的蛛丝马迹
Do we have a bead on Scylla yet?

04:17.570 --> 04:22.300
我们的安全和未来  均命悬一线
Our security, our future stands at a great precipice.

04:22.370 --> 04:24.370
到底有还是没有  乔纳森
It's a yes-or-no question, Jonathan.

04:25.730 --> 04:28.300
我们不想听你自言自语
And we don't need a soliloquy.

04:29.730 --> 04:33.430
霍华德  你去我办公室等我
Howard, why don't you wait in my office?

04:33.500 --> 04:39.700
不  我来此 是确保这次行动不会再出差错
No. I'm in here making sure this operation isn't fumbled as well.

04:41.500 --> 04:45.270
马上出去
Out... now.

04:45.330 --> 04:46.800
你有什么计划  乔纳森
What's your plan, Jonathan?

04:48.330 --> 04:51.670
我们来不就是为了这个吗
That's what we're all here for, right?

04:51.730 --> 04:55.330
你不听我们的箴言 执意转移"锡拉"  如今弄巧成拙
You tried to move Scylla over our better judgment, and it backfired,

04:55.400 --> 04:57.170
就认了吧
so spill it.

05:21.230 --> 05:23.830
还有其他问题吗
Any further questions?

05:25.930 --> 05:28.000
很好
Very well.

05:28.070 --> 05:29.400
你们都知道自己的任务了
You have your assignments.

05:29.470 --> 05:33.530
竭尽所能  今天就把"锡拉"找回来
Access your assets and retrieve Scylla today.

05:48.330 --> 05:50.370
赛尔夫探员  过去几个月里
Yeah, well, a lot of people that believed in me

05:50.430 --> 05:54.900
很多相信我的人 现在都死了
in the last few months, Agent Self, not all of them are alive today.

05:54.970 --> 05:58.170
我不明白这句话
I can't shake that line.

05:58.230 --> 06:00.030
"走为上策"
"All that avails is flight."

06:26.700 --> 06:28.330
起来
Come on.

06:41.870 --> 06:43.300
给  拿着
Here, take that.

06:45.300 --> 06:50.000
莎拉是对的  我们得送你去医院
Sara's right. We need to get you to a hospital now.

06:50.070 --> 06:55.270
我们就差那么一点 就那么一点
We were so close to the finish line. So close.

06:55.330 --> 06:56.730
我知道  我明白
Yeah, I know, I know, I know.

06:56.800 --> 07:04.470
我昨天给LJ打了电话 告诉他一切都接近尾声了
Listen, I, uh, I spoke to LJ yesterday. Told him this was almost over.

07:06.230 --> 07:08.930
我要对我儿子信守诺言
I'm keeping my word to my son, Michael.

07:10.870 --> 07:12.600
我早该发现这个阴谋
I should have seen this coming.

07:12.670 --> 07:19.130
不  这不是任何人的错 是赛尔夫耍了我们
No, no, it's no one's fault. Self played all of us.

07:19.200 --> 07:23.330
我们得离开这里 这是我们最后的选择
We gotta get out of here. This is our last option.

07:27.570 --> 07:29.370
好的
Yeah.

07:45.770 --> 07:48.700
-查看楼上  -安全
Take upstairs.Clear.

07:48.700 --> 07:49.700
安全
It's clear.

07:55.100 --> 07:58.300
现在知道我们的处境了
Now we know where we stand.

07:58.370 --> 08:00.130
走吧
Let's go.

08:05.300 --> 08:06.300
喂
Hello.

08:06.370 --> 08:07.870
迈克尔·斯科菲尔德
Michael Scofield.

08:07.930 --> 08:09.030
是的
Yes.

08:09.100 --> 08:12.070
我是贺勃·斯坦顿  国土安全局的
Herb Stanton, Department of Homeland Security.

08:12.130 --> 08:13.970
我们想谈谈
We want to talk.

08:14.030 --> 08:15.800
你们能不能回仓库
Can you please come back to the warehouse?

08:15.870 --> 08:19.870
没问题  但首先得给我们一些保障
All right, but first we're gonna need some assurances.

08:19.930 --> 08:21.700
你指什么
What kind of assurances?

08:21.770 --> 08:23.670
我们遵守了我们的诺言
Look, we held up our end of the deal,

08:23.730 --> 08:26.530
所以  我们要你 履行协议里的条件
so we're gonna need you to honor the terms of our agreements.

08:26.600 --> 08:28.570
那我得重新看一下那些条件
Well, I'd have to take another look at those terms,

08:28.630 --> 08:30.830
但我确定里面不包括偷走"锡拉"
but I'm fairly certain it didn't include stealing Scylla

08:30.900 --> 08:34.900
和冷血杀害两名联邦探员
or killing two federal agents in cold blood.

08:34.970 --> 08:36.770
你这话是什么意思
What are you talking about?

08:36.830 --> 08:39.970
我给你们准备了 一些新的条件
Here are the new terms I'm prepared to offer.

08:40.030 --> 08:42.200
回来  自首
Come back, turn yourselves in...

08:42.270 --> 08:44.270
等等  是赛尔夫算计了我们
Wait a minute! Self set us up!

08:44.330 --> 08:48.500
否则 我会追捕你们到天涯海角
Don't, and I'll hunt you down like animals.

