39:56.110 --> 39:57.680
2个还活着
about this operation. Two of them are still alive.

39:57.750 --> 39:59.610
一个跑了  我是另一个
One is now on the run. and I'm the other.

39:59.680 --> 40:01.650
我会守口如瓶
And I'm not saying a word.

40:01.710 --> 40:03.250
你休想轻易脱身  议员
You're not getting off that easy, Senator.

40:03.310 --> 40:05.380
你要帮我们
You are going to help us.

40:08.710 --> 40:11.810
会议桌上有个手提包
There is a folder in that briefcase

40:11.880 --> 40:13.310
包里有份文件
on the conference table.

40:13.380 --> 40:14.410
里面记录了
It contains

40:14.480 --> 40:16.680
这次行动的遗留问题
the last remnants of this operation.

40:16.750 --> 40:18.610
一旦你们把它处理掉
Once you dispose of it

40:18.680 --> 40:21.850
一切都不会发生
none of this ever existed.

40:21.910 --> 40:23.550
这是秘密行动的
That's the saving grace

40:23.610 --> 40:24.750
的好处
of a covert operation.

40:24.810 --> 40:26.080
如果你们想要
If you want...

40:27.680 --> 40:30.550
可以当作没发生过
...it never happened.

40:33.250 --> 40:36.280
我现在要走了
I'm going to walk away now.

40:36.350 --> 40:38.510
赶一趟航班
Catch a flight.

40:38.580 --> 40:40.280
可能在我妻子
Maybe see my wife

40:40.350 --> 40:42.250
睡觉前能赶到
before she goes to bed.

40:44.310 --> 40:46.510
我只希望出去时
I only hope I don't catch a bullet in the back

40:46.580 --> 40:47.550
不会背后来一枪
on my way out.

40:49.780 --> 40:51.780
我很抱歉  先生们
I'm really very sorry, gentlemen.

40:54.580 --> 40:56.580
我们努力过了
We tried.

40:59.650 --> 41:01.950
我们努力过了
We tried.

41:02.010 --> 41:02.950
让他走
Let him go.

41:03.010 --> 41:03.980
林肯
Linc,

41:04.050 --> 41:04.980
让他走
let him go.

41:05.050 --> 41:05.980
