我们现在逃吗
We running now?

41:17.450 --> 41:18.910
你要是再这么做
I will kill you myself

41:18.980 --> 41:21.110
我会杀了我自己的
the next time you do something like that.

41:24.480 --> 41:26.450
马宏在哪
Where's Mahone?

41:26.510 --> 41:28.980
他不见了
He's gone.

41:42.210 --> 41:44.150
你把"锡拉"搞全了
Well, we can do business

41:44.210 --> 41:45.780
我们再交易
when you get the rest of Scylla.

41:45.850 --> 41:48.650
你说什么
What are you talking about?

41:50.210 --> 41:52.280
这是不完整的
It's incomplete.

41:52.350 --> 41:53.380
不完整  什么
Incom...? Wha--

41:53.450 --> 41:54.480
玩什么把戏
Who is this clown?

41:54.550 --> 41:56.280
-把戏  -对  把戏
Clown? Yeah, clown.

41:56.350 --> 42:00.550
少了一个部件  小子
There's a piece missing, slick.

42:00.610 --> 42:02.150
看  这里
Look. Here.

42:47.080 --> 42:49.050
你好啊  唐
Hello, Don.

42:49.110 --> 42:52.180
我想你拿了我的东西
I believe you have something that belongs to me.

42:54.210 --> 42:56.350
过来拿吧
Come and get it.
